# GitHub project shortlist

These are the strongest Primed Talent projects to turn into clean GitHub repos.

## 1. sql-reporting-and-query-optimisation
Best SQL-focused repo. Shows advanced SQL, conditional aggregation, null-safe reporting, optimisation, and dashboard-style filtering logic.

Included files:
- Advance SQL.sql
- query Optimization.sql
- Assignment 1 - The Null-Safe Reporting Query.sql
- Activity 1- The Conditional Aggregation Sprint.sql
- Task 2 - Optimizing a Date-Range Query.sql
- Task 2 - Optimizing with Partitioning Knowledge.sql
- Real-Time Scenario 1 - The Dynamic Dashboard Filter.sql
- Real-Time Scenario 2 - High-Frequency Customer Identification.sql

## 2. customer-churn-sales-analysis-python
Strong analyst repo. Shows pandas-based analysis, data refinement, end-to-end notebook work, and business datasets for churn and sales.

Included files:
- Data Story Battle.ipynb
- Labwork_DataRefinement.ipynb
- Labwork_endtoend.ipynb
- customer_churn.csv
- customer_purchases.csv
- customers.csv
- orders.csv
- products.csv
- sales_data.csv
- SampleSuperstore.csv

## 3. power-bi-executive-dashboards
Best dashboard repo. Shows Power BI storytelling, executive presentation style, and dataset-backed dashboard work.

Included files:
- Activity 1 - The Executive Pitch.pbix
- Topic8_Simulatedscenerio.pbix
- Sample - Superstore.csv
- Data_Storytelling_and_Dashboard_Mastery.pdf
- Data_Visualization_Mastery.pdf

## 4. database-design-sql-and-powerbi
Good mixed repo. Shows database design, joins, SQL exercises, and Power BI dashboards tied to business reporting data.

Included files:
- Accounts_DB_1.sql
- Ecommerce_DB_1.sql
- Joins_db.sql
- Orders_db.sql
- Topic_6_Exercise2.ipynb
- Customer Demographics.pbix
- Dashboard design.pbix
- Data Story Pitch.pbix
- retail_sales.csv
- monthly_revenue_data.csv
- website_traffic_marketing_data.csv
- README.md

## 5. ames-housing-regression-analysis
Bonus repo. Shows regression and predictive analytics. Useful as a fifth project, but analyst repos above should come first.

Included files:
- Project AmesHousing.ipynb
- EDA+Graded+Exercise.ipynb
- AmesHousing.csv
- house_price_linear_regression_model.joblib

Start with the first 3 repos before adding the others.
